commit.message:
MeTee: bump version to 4.0.0

Update CHANGELOG.md

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Windows: initilaize variables

Initialize variables to make error paths work.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: conan: support higher version of the Linux compilers

Support up to gcc 12 and up to clang 15

Signed-off-by: Tomas Winkler <tomas.winkler@intel.com>

MeTee: add CONTRIBUTING.md file

Add CONTRIBUTING.md file.

Signed-off-by: Tomas Winkler <tomas.winkler@intel.com>

MeTee: linux: fix print in get handle

Make print in TeeGetDeviceHandle reflect the problem,
demote it to debug and add trailing newline.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: linux: do not set log if init failed

Avoid setting log level and log callback if init failed.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Windows: fix close on exit

Enable close on exit for init paths that
open file handle internally.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Windows: add missing newline

Add mising newline in log print.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: samples: add TRC sample

Add sample to TRC retrieval.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: tests: add GetTRC test

Add tests for GetTRC API.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: add GetTRC API

Add API to get TRC register value.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Linux: pull libmei 1.5.6

New gettrc API.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: add init api with all parameters

Add new API TeeInitFull to replace all Init variants.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: samples: return log level to original

Return log level to original one after log level sample.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: samples: add log callback to sample

Add log callback to mkhi sample.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: tests: add log callback test

Test log callback setter.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: add option for log callback

Add option to route all logs to the callback function
provided by caller.
If this function pointer is not defined, usual log routing
will be kept.
Add new APIs for init with log level and callback and
for log callback setting.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Linux: import libmei 1.5.5

Import libmei with log callback.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Linux: fix timeout treatment

Treat timeout as milliseconds, do not convert from seconds.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: log: demote FUNC_ENTRY/EXIT to debug

Avoid printing entry/exit log as error.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: windows: replace spaces with tabs

Fix formatting.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: samples: use stdbool on windows

Include stdbool.h with MSVC

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: CMake: disable doc build by default

Do not build Doxygen doc by default.
Let builder enable it when required.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: git: add full VS gitignore

Ignore all VS tailings.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: CMake: drop system ver requirement

Without this line IntelliSense can find Windows includes.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: CMake: add preset for full debug build

Add CMake preset to build debug with samples and tests.

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: bump version to 3.2.4

Update CHANGELOG.md

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: Linux: pull in libmei 1.5.4

Take the latest libmei sources with fix for reconnect in error state..

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>

MeTee: README: small cleanups

Add nproc explanation, refine grammar and formatting

Signed-off-by: Alexander Usyskin <alexander.usyskin@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Tomas Winkler <tomas.winkler@intel.com>

MeTee: linux: Include poll.h instead of sys/poll.h

fix compilation error with musl C library:

 error: #warning redirecting incorrect #include <sys/poll.h> to <poll.h>

Signed-off-by: Lee Chee Yang <chee.yang.lee@intel.com>
